---
// Philosophy section - editorial layout with large text and image
---

<section class="philosophy" aria-labelledby="philosophy-heading">
  <div class="philosophy__inner container">
    <div class="philosophy__text-col">
      <p class="label label-accent reveal">设计理念</p>
      <h2 id="philosophy-heading" class="philosophy__heading reveal reveal-delay-1">
        景观是<br>
        <em class="h-en">dialogue</em><br>
        大地与人的对话
      </h2>
      <div class="philosophy__body reveal reveal-delay-2">
        <p>张涵相信，真正优秀的景观设计不是在土地上强加秩序，而是倾听场地的记忆与自然的语言。每一处地形的起伏、每一束穿林的光影，都是设计的素材，也是设计的边界。</p>
        <p>从天府平原到巴山渝水，从城市屋顶到滨江廊道——十余年的实践让我们学会以低调的姿态介入，以长远的眼光布局，让自然过程与人的生活在时间中共同完成一件作品。</p>
      </div>
      <div class="philosophy__stats reveal reveal-delay-3">
        <div class="stat">
          <span class="stat__number">18</span>
          <span class="stat__unit">年</span>
          <span class="stat__label">从业经验</span>
        </div>
        <div class="stat__divider" aria-hidden="true"></div>
        <div class="stat">
          <span class="stat__number">200<span class="stat__plus">+</span></span>
          <span class="stat__label">完成项目</span>
        </div>
        <div class="stat__divider" aria-hidden="true"></div>
        <div class="stat">
          <span class="stat__number">12</span>
          <span class="stat__label">覆盖城市</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="philosophy__image-col reveal reveal-delay-1">
      <div class="philosophy__image-wrap">
        <img
          src="https://picsum.photos/seed/philosophy-1/900/1100"
          alt="景观设计现场"
          width="900"
          height="1100"
          loading="lazy"
        />
        <div class="philosophy__image-caption">
          <span class="label">天府中央公园 · 2024</span>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="philosophy__image-secondary reveal reveal-delay-2">
        <img
          src="https://picsum.photos/seed/philosophy-2/600/400"
          alt="自然景观细节"
          width="600"
          height="400"
          loading="lazy"
        />
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
.philosophy {
  padding-block: var(--space-section);
  background: var(--color-bg);
  overflow: hidden;
}

.philosophy__inner {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
  gap: clamp(3rem, 6vw, 8rem);
  align-items: center;
}

.philosophy__text-col {
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  gap: var(--space-8);
}

.philosophy__heading {
  font-family: var(--font-serif-cn);
  font-size: var(--text-xl);
  font-weight: 300;
  line-height: 1.2;
  letter-spacing: 0.04em;
  color: var(--color-ink);
}

.philosophy__heading em {
  font-family: var(--font-serif-en);
  font-style: italic;
  font-size: 1.2em;
  color: var(--color-accent);
  display: block;
  line-height: 1.1;
}

.philosophy__body {
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  gap: var(--space-4);
  color: var(--color-ink-muted);
  font-size: var(--text-sm);
  line-height: 1.9;
  max-width: 48ch;
}

.philosophy__stats {
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  gap: var(--space-8);
  padding-top: var(--space-8);
  border-top: 1px solid oklch(14% 0.01 60 / 0.1);
}

.stat {
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  gap: 2px;
}

.stat__number {
  font-family: var(--font-serif-en);
  font-size: clamp(2rem, 1.5rem + 2vw, 3rem);
  font-weight: 300;
  color: var(--color-ink);
  line-height: 1;
}

.stat__unit {
  font-family: var(--font-serif-cn);
  font-size: var(--text-lg);
  font-weight: 300;
  color: var(--color-ink);
  vertical-align: baseline;
}

.stat__plus {
  font-size: 0.6em;
  color: var(--color-accent);
  vertical-align: super;
}

.stat__label {
  font-family: var(--font-sans);
  font-size: var(--text-xs);
  color: var(--color-ink-faint);
  letter-spacing: 0.1em;
}

.stat__divider {
  width: 1px;
  height: 48px;
  background: oklch(14% 0.01 60 / 0.12);
  flex-shrink: 0;
}

/* Image column */
.philosophy__image-col {
  position: relative;
}

.philosophy__image-wrap {
  position: relative;
  border-radius: var(--radius-md);
  overflow: hidden;
  aspect-ratio: 9/11;
}

.philosophy__image-wrap img {
  width: 100%;
  height: 100%;
  object-fit: cover;
  transition: transform 0.8s var(--ease-out-expo);
}

.philosophy__image-wrap:hover img {
  transform: scale(1.03);
}

.philosophy__image-caption {
  position: absolute;
  bottom: var(--space-4);
  left: var(--space-4);
  background: oklch(14% 0.01 60 / 0.65);
  backdrop-filter: blur(8px);
  padding: var(--space-2) var(--space-4);
  border-radius: var(--radius-sm);
  color: rgba(255,255,255,0.7);
}

.philosophy__image-secondary {
  position: absolute;
  bottom: -2rem;
  right: -2rem;
  width: 55%;
  border-radius: var(--radius-md);
  overflow: hidden;
  box-shadow: 0 24px 48px oklch(14% 0.01 60 / 0.18);
  border: 4px solid var(--color-bg);
}

.philosophy__image-secondary img {
  width: 100%;
  height: 100%;
  object-fit: cover;
  aspect-ratio: 3/2;
}

@media (max-width: 900px) {
  .philosophy__inner {
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
  }

  .philosophy__image-col {
    order: -1;
  }

  .philosophy__image-secondary {
    display: none;
  }

  .philosophy__image-wrap {
    aspect-ratio: 16/9;
  }
}

@media (max-width: 640px) {
  .philosophy__stats {
    gap: var(--space-6);
  }
}
</style>
